# Commands Learned

Build image

```bash
docker build -t image_name:tag .
```

List images

```bash
docker images
```

View image history

```bash
docker history image_name
```

Delete image

```bash
docker rmi image_name
```

Create another tag

```bash
docker tag old_image:newtag new_image:newtag
```

